nd design-based simulations. In the application to the city level\ngrouped income data of Japan, we complete the patchy maps of the Gini\ncoefficient as well as mean income across the country.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Mar 2019 02:53:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 07:00:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-20"}
