mplicated situation\nrelating to the use of the theory of relativity and, in particular, Wigner\nrotation theory, in accelerator physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Mar 2019 13:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-19"}
